d data.","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,1030],"id":"b2e89f51-e0a5-75fe-c3b0-8dce9e68c66a","name":"Note: Abort — Malformed Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Reason & Act (AI Agent)\n\nThe AI brain: reads the input, decides which attached tools to call (and in what order), then composes the answer.\n\nPorts: ①→ Shape Agent Output · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"8c385376-960b-181a-3b2e-6f57b4a3fd1b","name":"Note: Reason & Act (AI Agent)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Groq Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `llama-3.3-70b-versatile`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Reason & Act (AI Agent)** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 Groq API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[561,1090],"id":"d64cfe94-2e68-0eed-419c-573da5df7736","name":"Note: Groq Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Think It Through\n\nScratchpad tool: lets the agent reason step-by-step before acting.\n\nFeeds **Reason & Act (AI Agent)** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[561,1510],"id":"f64c3e32-0526-071e-bdc6-e1f1ed093fae","name":"Note: Think It Through"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Lookup API Data\n\nTool the agent can call to hit the REST API with parameters it chooses at runtime.\n\nFeeds **Reason & Act (AI Agent)** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[790,1750],"id":"9fb43a7d-3de6-47f3-a08e-05574b9efe7b","name":"Note: Lookup API Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Conversation Memory\n\nConversation memory keyed by session — the bot remembers earlier turns for each user separately.\n\nFeeds **Reason & Act (AI Agent)** as `memory`\n\n🔑 Postgres connection","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[547,1810],"id":"482968c1-b577-9b10-b9de-42f921c46993","name":"Note: Conversation Memory"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Shape Agent Output\n\nShapes the item: writes `answer`, `confidence`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Confident Enough?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1114,520],"id":"43b920ab-8094-d7ca-1795-80e67f2ea275","name":"Note: Shape Agent Output"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Confident Enough?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.confidence }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Deliver Answer + Log to Notion · ②→ Escalate to Human Queue","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1438,520],"id":"fe60ffee-eabf-f24d-d69b-726a3d6a3ee9","name":"Note: Confident Enough?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Deliver Answer + Log to Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Join Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1762,280],"id":"72b08ed6-0fd1-68cc-499c-9bf4a264e589","name":"Note: Deliver Answer + Log to Notion"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate to Human Queue\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Join Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2086,880],"id":"5832b050-576d-a066-0dee-da8d82ddcffe","name":"Note: Escalate to Human Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Join Outcomes\n\nRejoins 2 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2734,520],"id":"2dea5753-a47e-1ba3-0733-dced57e675b0","name":"Note: Join Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3706,520],"id":"6489921c-bc92-1216-4233-17a2274741c8","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4030,520],"id":"fad36334-959e-cee6-39ac-ab2d985289fd","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4354,520],"id":"819b7654-9dfa-f25a-0f2b-d552fb81dba7","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4678,520],"id":"05fd5379-f1d3-0cba-d464-6be86c3b572b","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5002,520],"id":"2cbb73b2-491e-14b0-a541-732ab7f49b52","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5326,520],"id":"261e2d30-6d42-ad5f-2a75-ccc63966a9ef","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5650,520],"id":"c2a7b365-bb15-b2bc-5c62-55f4d20463b9","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Fingerprint for Idempotency","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5974,520],"id":"ba70a27c-ac4a-bfa0-348c-8990d0db1163","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per request (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6298,520],"id":"5df4d447-126c-cc6f-722e-a4e7435c7208","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6622,520],"id":"6e74c629-7ff2-c52e-fa3d-1a41c42679f7","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6946,520],"id":"54b76f99-0202-c6b9-906c-b1cdb1fcf8ce","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7270,520],"id":"9d10d8d5-4254-9887-c0b9-4454efd4ae9f","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7594,520],"id":"61434c7e-9265-aa1c-8fd6-6eea5c470524","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Notion)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7918,520],"id":"370eeb90-e83a-902f-ce14-9f351ab477a5","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Notion)\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8242,520],"id":"fa00117f-13d6-3fd1-ad9e-14115d2aed88","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Notion)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8566,520],"id":"1262b985-351d-421f-630b-c02d5817c8d9","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7918,1540],"id":"554c1874-4be5-fd3a-c85f-778e7c5a6c69","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8242,1540],"id":"a8941184-51c4-60f8-5c42-61b21aa2a8e3","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8566,1540],"id":"46aba151-58b3-5c44-fd3c-d26c57b2a1f8","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Reply to chat messages for your team for Multi-Tool Agent\n\n**Pattern:** Chatbot Responder · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Chat\n\n## What it does\nReply to chat messages for your team for Multi-Tool Agent. It responds live to chat messages.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual multi-tool agent is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWhen Chat Message Received → Required Fields Present? → Reason & Act (AI Agent) → Shape Agent Output → Confident Enough? → Deliver Answer + Log to Notion → Join Outcomes → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to chatbot responder without manual effort\n- Anyone automating multi-tool agent in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account; Groq API key; Notion integration token; Postgres connection; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"7f6b9592-38b6-2cec-e839-a0a30ba710ba","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"d5512998-5fb6-9c40-0d7b-4b70fc6d604e","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"78cd3cd8-a25c-5b1e-b635-a4ac3d20d820","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"92ed4950-5a4a-a45a-758d-5230ff4f7839","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your multi-tool agent process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-260],"id":"f84c11f7-35fa-cc80-75d6-f53fd4d9da2e","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"When Chat Message Received":{"main":[[{"node":"Required Fields Present?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Required Fields Present?":{"main":[[{"node":"Reason & Act (AI Agent)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Abort — Malformed Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Groq Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Reason & Act (AI Agent)","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Think It Through":{"ai_tool":[[{"node":"Reason & Act (AI Agent)","type":"ai_tool","index":0}]]},"Lookup API Data":{"ai_tool":[[{"node":"Reason & Act (AI Agent)","type":"ai_tool","index":0}]]},"Conversation Memory":{"ai_memory":[[{"node":"Reason & Act (AI Agent)","type":"ai_memory","index":0}]]},"Reason & Act (AI Agent)":{"main":[[{"node":"Shape Agent Output","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Shape Agent Output":{"main":[[{"node":"Confident Enough?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Confident Enough?":{"main":[[{"node":"Deliver Answer + Log to Notion","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Escalate to Human Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Deliver Answer + Log to Notion":{"main":[[{"node":"Join Outcomes","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate to Human Queue":{"main":[[{"node":"Join Outcomes","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Join Outcomes":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Notion)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Notion)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"fd1b0135-d47a-46d3-8126-beb0b05d792d","id":"FDX00762"}